eaths from kidney failure]]\n[[Category:American people of Jewish descent]]\n[[Category:Boys High School (Brooklyn) alumni]]\n[[Category:People convicted of obscenity]]\n[[Category:People from Far Rockaway, Queens]]\n[[Category:People from the Upper East Side]]\n", "name_user": "Iridescent", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eLegal issues and financial woes:Cleanup andtypo fixing,typo(s) fixed: 2005-08 \u2192 2005\u201308", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Al_Goldstein"}
